title: Cephalic Carnage - Lucid Interval (2002)
description:
I\&#039;ve only recently been introduced to Cephalic Carnage, but I believe that they are indeed worthy of an upload.  Lucid Interval is a true trip through some incredible metal, from start to finish.  Time and time again throughout the CD, this band proves that they are truly interesting Grindcore/Death Metal band worthy of listening to.  So here\&#039;s the track list
